## Verify

```sh
make verify-generated
```

Or run `go test ./...` in `backend`{{if .Frontend}} and `pnpm typecheck && pnpm test && pnpm build` in `frontend`{{end}}.

See [the architecture guide](./docs/architecture.md) and [testing guide](./docs/testing.md).
